name: ForTheWeebs
description:
Hi, this is my first attempt at a merge.
I take no credit at all, took me literally 5 seconds and I just did it out of curiosity and to learn.
This is a mix between Kuromimix, Nyanmix and Pastelmix.
I think it looks pretty neat and hopefully you agree.
I've got no idea about anything more than the result looking good.
As for VAE, I baked in Pastelmix VAE but while creating an image I use Nyanmix VAE.
Feel free to do whatever you want with what you create using this model, but don't take money from others in return for giving out this model. This merge is and should always be free.
I hope you enjoy :).
